\begin_layout Standard
欧几里得空间的正交变换有：
\begin_inset Formula $\sin(\theta)^{2}+\cos(\theta)^{2}=1$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

想象对矢量
\begin_inset Formula $(1,0)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $(0,1)$
\end_inset

逆时针转动
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

角度，得到新矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\cos\theta,\sin\theta\right)$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(-\sin\theta,\cos\theta\right)$
\end_inset

，分别对应转动矩阵的第一列和第二列：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\cos(\theta) & -\sin(\theta)\\
\sin(\theta) & \cos(\theta)
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
类似地，我们知道
\begin_inset Formula $\cosh(\theta)=\frac{e^{\theta}+e^{-\theta}}{2}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\sinh(\theta)=\frac{e^{\theta}-e^{-\theta}}{2}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\cosh(\theta)^{2}-\sinh(\theta)^{2}=1$
\end_inset

,所以设逆变矢量的变换矩阵为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\cosh(\theta) & -\sinh(\theta)\\
-\sinh(\theta) & \cosh(\theta)
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

在闵可夫斯基度规下，即可保证正交性，又可保证按度规归一化。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在速度表象下，实际上是，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\beta & =\sqrt{1-v^{2}}\\
\gamma & =1/\beta=1/\sqrt{1-v^{2}}\ge1
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $1/\gamma^{2}=1-v^{2}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{2}-\left(\frac{v}{\beta}\right)^{2}=1$
\end_inset

,也就是
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{2}-\gamma^{2}v^{2}=1$
\end_inset

所以，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta=\ln\left(\frac{\gamma+\gamma v}{2}\right)=\frac{1}{2}\ln\left(\frac{\left(1+v\right)^{2}}{2(1-v^{2})}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
x^{\prime}\\
t^{\prime}
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\gamma & -\gamma v\\
-\gamma v & \gamma
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
x\\
t
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

 这里的负号是一种约定，跟坐标系的手性有关。逆变矢量就这么变，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

这里虽然写的是指标上下收缩的形式，但是相乘的时候，就按普通的矩阵乘法。负号已经考虑在矩阵里面了。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
推导速度表象下的表示形式
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{\mu}=\Lambda^{\mu\nu}g_{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

洛伦兹变换矩阵如何用速度
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

表示，A坐标系静止，B坐标系以速度
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

向右匀速移动，同时考察B坐标系的原点，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
t^{\prime}\\
0
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a & b\\
b & a
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
t\\
vt
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a\frac{t}{t^{\prime}}=\frac{1}{1-v^{2}}\label{eq:1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
同时考虑洛伦兹矩阵的逆矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & x^{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}\\
\Rightarrow & \Lambda i_{\phantom{\mu}\mu}^{\nu}x^{\prime\mu}=x^{\nu}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
根据定义有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\delta_{\phantom{\rho}\sigma}^{\rho} & =\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}\delta_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\mu}\\
 & \Rightarrow\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}(\Lambda^{\perp})_{\phantom{\sigma}\sigma}^{\mu}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里不是普通的矩阵相乘，这里的相乘是指标收缩，也就是带度规的运算，如果要变成普通矩阵相乘，还需要乘上相应的
\begin_inset Formula $\pm1$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

所以认为洛伦兹矩阵的逆矩阵是它的转置再乘上相应的度规（时间分量符号不变，空间分量
\begin_inset Formula $-1$
\end_inset

）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
t\\
vt
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a & -b\\
-b & a
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
t^{\prime}\\
0
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
t=at^{\prime}\Rightarrow\frac{t}{t^{\prime}}=a
\]

\end_inset

结合EQ:
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
